com.rjrudin.marklogic.modulesloader.impl

Class DefaultModulesLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rjrudin.marklogic.client.LoggingObject
      • com.rjrudin.marklogic.modulesloader.impl.DefaultModulesLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModulesLoader

    public class DefaultModulesLoader
extends LoggingObject
implements ModulesLoader
    Uses the REST API for loading all modules except "assets", which are loaded via XCC for speed reasons. Note that this class will not be threadsafe since XccAssetLoader is not currently threadsafe either.
